    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/av44544186" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考</a></p><h1 id="0-下载Git"><a href="#0-下载Git" class="headerlink" title="0. 下载Git"></a>0. 下载<a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git</a></h1><p>一路默认安装（安装完系统自动将它添加到环境变量了）</p><h1 id="1-下载nodejs-cn-或-nodejs-org-en"><a href="#1-下载nodejs-cn-或-nodejs-org-en" class="headerlink" title="1.下载nodejs.cn 或 nodejs.org/en"></a>1.下载<a href="http://nodejs.cn/download/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nodejs.cn</a> 或 <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nodejs.org/en</a></h1><p>一路默认安装<br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-bf291ddd0e7d8b81.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v   <span class="comment">//验证是否成功安装</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https:<span class="comment">//registry.npm.taobao.org   //把npm的仓库切换到国内taobao仓库</span></span><br><span class="line">cnpm   <span class="comment">//后面关于npm的命令均改为cnpm</span></span><br><span class="line">cnpm -v</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo - v</span><br><span class="line">cd /d <span class="string">"E:\blog"</span>       <span class="comment">//进入在想要建立博客的路径下</span></span><br><span class="line">mkdir codepig    <span class="comment">//新建文件夹codepig</span></span><br><span class="line">cd /d codepig  <span class="comment">//这个文件里必须什么都没有，不然下一步出错</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init   <span class="comment">//hexo初始化，比较慢，可以换成热点</span></span><br><span class="line">cnpm install   <span class="comment">//安装依赖</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo s   <span class="comment">//输入出现的网址在浏览器打开,用来预览，</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo n <span class="string">"我的第一篇博客文章"</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//在typora中写博客</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo c  <span class="comment">//clear清除</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g  <span class="comment">//generate生成</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s     <span class="comment">////输入出现的网址在浏览器打开,刷新网页进行预览</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-e9cb8fc13877a52c.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-8ec6b3403d1611d9.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-6674c2f9d182ad64.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><h1 id="2-下载typora"><a href="#2-下载typora" class="headerlink" title="2.下载typora"></a>2.下载<a href="https://typora.io/#windows" target="_blank" rel="noopener">typora</a></h1><p>用typora直接就可以打开md文件，然后在其里面修改需要在博客里面要些的内容<br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-80febee0cae8be01.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><h1 id="3-将博客部署到github上公开使用"><a href="#3-将博客部署到github上公开使用" class="headerlink" title="3. 将博客部署到github上公开使用"></a>3. 将博客部署到github上公开使用</h1><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-78f53b8e478aa8e4.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /d <span class="string">"E:\blog\codepig"</span> </span><br><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git    <span class="comment">//在E:\blog\codepig目录下安装git工具</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-4ff92f301e75b73a.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-ba9aa86577d6dbdc.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><p>出错后将git添加到环境变量中<br><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-f6d5ae3a19218b80.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d    <span class="comment">//重新执行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-50ed3fcd466a5f36.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-9e7c8f6087ad0264.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-3afcd1adce5ba2f2.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-37f17c2d49d332c3.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><h1 id="4-更换博客主题"><a href="#4-更换博客主题" class="headerlink" title="4. 更换博客主题"></a>4. 更换博客主题</h1><blockquote><p>主题网站<br><a href="https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">推荐</a><br><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/nBkICDydd3bGvYYYhyXBmw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">6 步走，让你的个人博客「更极客」！</a><br><a href="https://youngerli.github.io/2017/11/21/Hexo%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%B1%9E%E4%BA%8E%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">李扬</a></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:<span class="comment">//github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/12426161-07335fb573e7e6de.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240" alt="image.png"></p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /d themes/next</span><br><span class="line">git pull</span><br><span class="line">cd /d <span class="string">"E:\blog\codepig"</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo c   <span class="comment">// 清除缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g  <span class="comment">//生成静态网页文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d  <span class="comment">//部署网站</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="设置动态背景"><a href="#设置动态背景" class="headerlink" title="设置动态背景"></a>设置动态背景</h1><p><a href="http://www.xudajian.com/2017/07/30/hexo-%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">参考</a></p><h1 id="隐藏博客下面图标"><a href="#隐藏博客下面图标" class="headerlink" title="隐藏博客下面图标"></a>隐藏博客下面图标</h1><p><img